  "title": "Whakatane",
  "summary": "短途游又来了。这次是四天三晚。 Kaputerangi lookout，这里很漂亮。尤其是云彩的影子。 住的民 […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-171.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>短途游又来了。这次是四天三晚。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-173.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Kaputerangi lookout，这里很漂亮。尤其是云彩的影子。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-170.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>住的民宿也不错。早上的golden hour随便出去拍拍。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-176.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>民宿坐落于岛上，半个岛都是房东的。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-175.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>风景很不错，提供的早餐也很好。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-174.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>当然还有一条可爱的狗。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-178.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Golden hour的露水。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-177.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>虚化的效果很魔幻。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-168.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Government Gardens里面的房子。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-172.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>去的时候在施工，这两张还是隔着栅栏拍的。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-179.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Playground的麻绳，很有节奏。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-180.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>沙子纹理，一向是我喜欢拍的。感觉这个题材已经多到可以整理出来成一本相册。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-169.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
  "image": "https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-173.png",
